Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.65,1:02:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个问题 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:37.72,1:02:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然三次都有做 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:41.05,1:02:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常会手淫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.06,1:02:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是你问出未的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:47.33,1:02:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手淫有时有 有时没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:53.87,1:02:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候会手淫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:56.27,1:02:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候 当然是想做的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.67,1:03:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样 具体我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:01.74,1:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是每天都做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:05.35,1:03:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:08.28,1:03:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的时候就会那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:14.02,1:03:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉才会手淫 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:21.50,1:03:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有其他的了 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:23.90,1:03:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:28.70,1:03:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想过要自慰的时候吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:33.24,1:03:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时也不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:35.64,1:03:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候会耗损体力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:38.31,1:03:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:41.11,1:03:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:47.65,1:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习的时候吧  练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:53.93,1:03:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在家里练习过吗 有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:57.00,1:03:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习不知什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:59.13,1:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习的时候不会得到太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:01.80,1:04:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很值得一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:04.47,1:04:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看的时侯看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:06.34,1:04:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像是茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:07.81,1:04:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用电棒喷出来的 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:11.15,1:04:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好装扮一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:12.61,1:04:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装扮的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.55,1:04:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次够没有太过于注重装扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:17.15,1:04:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很丰满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:20.09,1:04:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛的感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:21.56,1:04:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:23.16,1:04:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不停下来 哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:26.76,1:04:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到喷出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:28.76,1:04:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:31.57,1:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怼进小穴的玩具什么的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:35.70,1:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有，有的 有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:39.31,1:04:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这次 恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:41.44,1:04:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一次喷水的快感 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:46.25,1:04:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一个用自慰的喷水
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:50.78,1:04:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷水
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:52.79,1:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想要 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:55.19,1:04:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有可以使用的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:59.46,1:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:01.20,1:05:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是怎么使用它喷出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:13.61,1:05:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己未哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:29.22,1:05:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话喷不出来 自己也会在网上调查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:36.70,1:05:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有很想要的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:40.57,1:05:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为怼进去了 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:44.17,1:05:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己不努力的话 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:46.57,1:05:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不调查自己根本不知道 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:48.71,1:05:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为这个 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:51.38,1:05:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在洗澡的时候也有练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:54.45,1:05:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷出来的话感觉很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:57.12,1:05:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张的时候会很难受 那个时候的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:59.79,1:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:01.26,1:06:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种感觉 什么感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:04.86,1:06:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不紧张的感觉 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:10.60,1:06:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种感觉 进行下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:28.62,1:06:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:35.82,1:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:42.07,1:10:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:57.95,1:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:01.96,1:11:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.16,1:11:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:26.25,1:11:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:28.92,1:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 果然来不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:32.79,1:11:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是出来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:34.66,1:11:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 好多好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:36.79,1:11:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉很厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:51.21,1:11:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样俘获了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:55.08,1:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:56.81,1:11:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也很吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:58.41,1:12:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也非常吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:04.82,1:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:06.02,1:12:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:10.42,1:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一湿润就出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:16.96,1:12:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉可以的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.03,1:12:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道可以喷出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:24.17,1:12:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很惊讶的样子是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:32.31,1:12:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:33.25,1:12:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也可以喷出来 是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:35.92,1:12:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:38.85,1:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好气害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:42.19,1:12:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:45.79,1:12:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:50.06,1:12:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:51.27,1:12:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:52.47,1:12:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:53.93,1:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，总感觉好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.60,1:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:57.90,1:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经湿了一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:20.72,1:19:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:21.52,1:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:59.09,1:21:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:54.21,1:21:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊
